<br>
As for the AE's, granted we are only on HoT at the moment (not doing WToV yet), but our guild is melee heave, so usually at least 4 of a group have taken AE damage (can't hide from it) at any time.  As such our clerics use Ethereal Elixer usually...meaning even with fungi and higher health, I am not saving any mana because the group heal is used regardless.<br>
<br>
Granted I don't actually own a fungi outright, but different guildmembers used to loan one for our 2 weekly raids.  I stopped wearing it simply because it was not worth the AC/HP/stat loss as the regen was not that critical.  Even if I had one for XP grouping with my shaman, the fungi would go to him, not the monk, as he can turn it into far more hps than the fungi can with cannibalization.<br>
<br>
